Award Title: Norham Road Depot Extension & Refurbishment Project Ref 19-042 02. Internal Plastering & Suspended Ceilings
Award Description:
The Authority is seeking expressions of interest from suitably qualified and experienced Contractors to enter into a Contract (the Contract) for the Norham Road Depot Extension and Refurbishment project (the Works) to assist with the delivery of the Authority's Operational Depot Accommodation Project. This package of works is specifically relating to Internal Plastering & Suspended Ceilings.
The works are to be completed during the construction period 01/07/2020 to 20/11/2020.
